# Tidbits
<!-- ... --> is the format for HTML comments, which are not rendered when displayed on GitHub, so I can use this to make notes without it being visible to readers.

chmod values:
owner / group / everyone

read = 4
write = 2
execute = 1

600 - owner can read/write
644 - owner can read/write, group can read, everyone can read
700 - owner full access, nothing for anyone else
777 - everyone has full access. wide open.

